{
  "stem": "766.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So this what she wanted.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But at the same time, she didn't beat anybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But once, one girl, she-- I don't know what she did.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She ask her to-- to-- to knee, on one knee and put a glass of-- with water on the head.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And if she-- the-- the water shouldn't run off and spill out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So how long can you be, not to move?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I couldn't watch too much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because first of all, I couldn't watch either.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and I have to do something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this what she-- she was cruel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She didn't beat her, but it's worse than beaten.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So now my work, I had a double bookkeeping, the temperature.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had one for the German.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because every once in a while came a German, a doctor or some military man, in the uniform.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he asked me to show that so for him, everybody had good temperature.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They all had TB, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And other things too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I said, one had-- everybody had the skin.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And one had diarrhea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One had a cut here.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I didn't tell the truth.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I was risking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But so I risk.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I had to do something.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they would kill them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they would take them out right away, back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And do that again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So, all right, so this was the thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I had it over there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "After a while, they brought another transport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were a few Polish from my hometown.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I felt better because the Hungarians don't like Polish either, and I couldn't talk.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "All right, German doesn't matter to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So over there was one young girl.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was a-- a daughter of a doctor, my next-door neighbor.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I adopted her, like my child.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
